gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Timberwolves 119, Jazz 100
gameRecap.excerpt: Anthony Edwards led Minnesota with 31 points, 10 rebounds, five assists, three steals, and three blocks as the Timberwolves defeated the Jazz, 119-100. Mike Conley totaled a season-high 25 points while Naz Reid added 22 points, 12 rebounds, and five assists. Collin Sexton (22 points, 10 assists) and Keyonte George (18 points) led Utah in the loss. Minnesota improves to 46-21 as the Jazz move to 29-38.
